### 3.3.2   SPKI Public Key 

TODO: should the SPKI not include a version number?

From the NTRU Prime specification, the Streamlined NTRU Prime public key contains h, optionally encoding of h can be reduced with optional parameter d (check that this is in the Round 2 spec)

NTRUPrimePublicKey := ...SEQ...
  BIT STRING {
    SEQUENCE {
       h BIT STRING,   -- vector(p)
       d [0] IMPLICIT OPTIONAL {
         d  BOOL, 		-- tighter encoding option
       }
    }
  }

From the NTRU Prime specification, the Streamlined NTRU LPRime public key contains A, S

NTRULPRimePublicKey := ...SEQ...
  BIT STRING {
    SEQUENCE {
       A BIT STRING,
       S BIT STRING
    }
  }

